text:
Excited to announce I’m playing in eSoccer Aid on Saturday! 🎮⚽

@SoccerAid for @UNICEF_uk have teamed up with @EASPORTSFIFA to help stop impact of coronavirus on children’s lives 

Info here 👉 https://t.co/MztTDSEyPY https://t.co/roht3jrung

Was a pleasure to join my brother @Louis_Tomlinson for his judges house auditions, and of course the legend that is @nilerodgers 🙏🏼

Good luck to all of the contestants, I really enjoyed meeting you all and hearing you sing.

@TheXFactor on ITV, Saturday at 8.35pm &amp; Sunday at 8pm https://t.co/fu5WM4Yvp7
